-- LBMA Appoints Ruth Crowell Chief Executive Officer
-- B y   C l a u d i a   C a r p e n t e r
-- 2013-11-01T16:55:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-01/lbma-appoints-ruth-crowell-chief-executive-officer.html
Ruth Crowell will be chief executive
officer of the London Bullion Market Association, effective at
the end of December.  She replaces Stewart Murray who is retiring, the LBMA said
in an e-mailed press release today. Crowell was deputy CEO since
June 2012 and worked at the LBMA for seven years. The LBMA
represents the wholesale over-the-counter market for gold and
silver bullion.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  